{
  "stem": "21817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They used to say it's partisan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they brought them over over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "On one side was a small hill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They took off-- everybody had to take off the shoes and the clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They lined them up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "On one side was the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the other side was regular German soldiers with-- there were no machine-- They didn't use machine guns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They used regular rifles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And some of them, I could see they were crossing themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because they were so exhausted that they didn't ask.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were waiting they should, should, should get shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And finally, we could hear the, the shot from, from all those rifles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were behind over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So many young men were all killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[CRYING] They, they were all were killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some fell down in the ditch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were still on top.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to push them down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are we next?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But somehow, luckily, it looks like the human mind works different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did our job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they brought us back to the camp, to the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, knowing what's going on and seeing what's happening, I made up my mind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not going to be one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us back after that big execution.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For, for about a week or 10 days, they didn't take anybody to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Either they stopped shooting for a, for a few days, or they were usually gathering bigger groups.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they-- if they used to catch in the woods one or two, they used to put him in a prison.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a-- they made a prison in, in, in the, in the building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we used to go in the building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
